Revert "tcp: change RTO calculation"

This reverts commit d8e9f0a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e1f2a3b4c5d6e7.

The RTO change introduced in the above commit causes connection
stalls on high-latency satellite links. The issue is that the
new RTO calculation is too aggressive and triggers spurious
retransmissions.

Revert to the previous RTO calculation until a better fix is found.

